The Wolf Pup Process

Step 1: General Planning

Our team meets with the client to discuss their vision and develop an understanding of their needs. Will the page simply be a means of presenting information, or will there be other features like login / logout, Google Maps, and payment integration? By the end of this step, our team should have a solid understanding of the client's needs.

Step 2: Backend Models and Tables

This part is a little more technical, but here is where our team will create the backend models and database tables necessary to keep track of any persistent data such as usernames, passwords, emails, direct messages, profile pictures, etc.
